1
00:00:01,396 --> 00:00:03,202
Previously on
<i>The Secret Circle...</i>

2
00:00:04,727 --> 00:00:06,034
Aah!

3
00:00:06,036 --> 00:00:07,605
Cassie.

4
00:00:12,578 --> 00:00:14,757
I'm sorry
about your mom.

5
00:00:13,129 --> 00:00:14,695
Thanks.
Have you seen her yet?

6
00:00:14,697 --> 00:00:16,030
She got in yesterday.

7
00:00:16,032 --> 00:00:17,465
It's ok, Cassie.

8
00:00:17,467 --> 00:00:20,034
We're different.
You're different.

9
00:00:20,036 --> 00:00:23,421
You're a witch. You're
a full blooded, 100% witch.

10
00:00:23,423 --> 00:00:25,205
There's no such thing
as witches and magic.

11
00:00:25,207 --> 00:00:27,207
Are you doing this?

12
00:00:27,209 --> 00:00:29,143
We are.

13
00:00:33,982 --> 00:00:36,650
With her here, we
have real power now.

14
00:00:37,903 --> 00:00:40,438
Each family
has a book,

15
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:42,857
a journal that lays down each
family line.

16
00:00:42,859 --> 00:00:45,109
A complete circle is 6.

17
00:00:45,111 --> 00:00:46,527
You complete
the circle.

18
00:00:46,529 --> 00:00:47,695
Now we're whole.

19
00:00:47,697 --> 00:00:49,163
You are seriously
messed up.

20
00:00:49,165 --> 00:00:50,731
She's got the gift.

21
00:00:50,733 --> 00:00:53,868
Are you sure you can get
Cassie to do what we need?

22
00:00:53,870 --> 00:00:57,121
The circle will take care of that
without even knowing it.

23
00:01:01,426 --> 00:01:03,761
My sweet Cassie,

24
00:01:03,763 --> 00:01:05,763
I didn't want you
to have this life,

25
00:01:05,765 --> 00:01:09,249
but destiny's not
easy to run from.

26
00:01:12,471 --> 00:01:15,773
You have incredible power
inside you.

27
00:01:16,975 --> 00:01:19,593
People will come for it.

28
00:01:19,595 --> 00:01:21,762
They will come for you.

29
00:01:26,434 --> 00:01:29,537
I hoped that keeping this secret
would keep you safe,

30
00:01:29,539 --> 00:01:31,956
but all I've done
is left you unprotected.

31
00:01:35,110 --> 00:01:36,794
I know how alone
you must feel,

32
00:01:36,796 --> 00:01:38,579
but be careful
who you trust,

33
00:01:38,581 --> 00:01:40,998
even people who
call themselves friends.

34
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:44,618
Your power is the only thing
that can keep you safe.

35
00:02:09,727 --> 00:02:11,945
Give me light.

36
00:02:18,286 --> 00:02:20,787
Ok.

37
00:02:20,789 --> 00:02:23,857
Give me light.

38
00:02:33,467 --> 00:02:36,303
Give me light.

39
