But no one else
can get hurt.

546
00:33:04,241 --> 00:33:06,326
It's wrong.

547
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:10,334
Diana's right.

548
00:33:10,336 --> 00:33:13,890
We have to bind the circle.

549
00:33:14,893 --> 00:33:18,899
We'll be at
the beach at midnight.

550
