At first I thought he pushed
the children to form a circle

552
00:33:38,938 --> 00:33:43,111
and then used their power
to somehow reestablish his.

553
00:33:43,113 --> 00:33:47,135
But then I realized
Charles Meade is many things,

554
00:33:47,137 --> 00:33:49,840
clever is not
one of them.

555
00:33:49,842 --> 00:33:52,545
And then I saw you.

556
00:33:54,282 --> 00:33:58,089
You couldn't have saved that
girl tonight without a crystal.

557
00:33:58,091 --> 00:34:01,145
Where'd you get it?
They were all destroyed.

558
00:34:02,414 --> 00:34:04,969
It's wrong of you
to strip us of our power.

559
00:34:04,971 --> 00:34:07,056
