about with you and Cassie?

595
00:37:00,737 --> 00:37:02,789
Why would you
ask that?

596
00:37:02,791 --> 00:37:06,663
Because I'm insecure.

597
00:37:06,665 --> 00:37:10,169
And I love you.

598
00:37:12,759 --> 00:37:14,979
Come here.

599
