yourself.

612
00:38:34,711 --> 00:38:36,446
Come here.

613
00:38:37,751 --> 00:38:41,172
That girl could have
been you tonight.

614
00:38:45,515 --> 00:38:48,820
Everything's gonna
be ok, mom.

615
00:38:57,704 --> 00:38:59,790
Get in.
I'll take you there.

616
00:38:59,792 --> 00:39:01,626
I'm good.

617
00:39:02,764 --> 00:39:04,682
Seriously,
I want to walk.

618
00:39:04,684 --> 00:39:06,502
I like it.

619
00:39:06,504 --> 00:39:08,055
It's a nice night.

620
00:39:08,057 --> 00:39:09,558
